  block t4_header: TextBlock {
    content: @md # Promotional Product Usage
**Data gap — placeholder.** The current data mart does not include a promotions dimension, promotional-price flag, or transaction-line grain.

**To enable this dashboard the warehouse needs:**
- `dim_promotion` table (id, name, start/end, type)
- `is_promo_priced` flag on `fact_daily_sales` (or finer-grained `fact_transaction_lines`)
- Basket-level (transaction) grain for basket-size analyses

Once those are wired in, this tab will cover: full-price vs promo splits, time-of-day comparisons, basket size, and per-basket purchase distribution.;;
  }
  block t5_header: TextBlock {
    content: @md # Ad Hoc Analysis
Open exploration using the full-grain fact tables. Filter by date, venue, and category to drill into product, member, and category-mix questions.;;
  }
  block t5_filter_date: FilterBlock {
    label: 'Date'
    type: 'field'
